message.entry: The input to FMINBND should be either a structure with valid fields or consist of at least three arguments.
FMINBND only accepts inputs of data type double.
Invalid value for OPTIONS parameter MaxFunEvals. FMINBND requires MaxFunEvals to be a real non-negative integer (not a character vector).
Invalid value for OPTIONS parameter MaxIter. FMINBND requires MaxIter to be a real non-negative integer (not a character vector).
Exiting due to infeasibility: the lower bound exceeds the upper bound.
Optimization terminated:\n the current x satisfies the termination criteria using OPTIONS.TolX of {0} \n
User supplied objective function must return a scalar value.
